Package: BRDT
Type: Package
Title: Binomial Reliability Demonstration Tests (BRDT)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    c(person("Suiyao",
             "Chen",
             role = c("aut", "cre"),
             email = "csycsy12377@gmail.com"))
Maintainer: Suiyao Chen <csycsy12377@gmail.com>
Description: This is a implementation of design methods for binomial reliability demonstration tests (BRDT) with failure count data. 
    The acceptanace decision uncertainty of BRDT has been quantified and the impacts of the uncertainty on related reliability assurance activities 
    such as reliability growth and warranty services are evaluated. 
